scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collections contains the moving image and audio recordings produced or held by the National Education Association. The collection contains three series reflecting the recording's purpose. The three series are:
Conventions; Educational Material; and Promotional Material.

arrangement.head: Arrangement note
arrangement.p: Collection: Organized into 3 series: Conventions; Educational Material; and Promotional Material.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: This collection is open for research.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Series contains audio and moving image recordings from various conventions, conferences and workshops. Most of these recordings are from NEA conventions, the Annual Meeting/Representative Assembly prominent among them. The recordings include speakers, individual sessions, workshops, interviews and highlights.
